        <div class="body">
            <p>Limiting Zend_Locale based on a class which itself is based on Zend_Locale is nothing which should be implemented.</p>

<p>Other classes like Zend_Currency could be in need of informations which would then not be possible to provide when there are limitations based on a non Locale class.</p>

<p>When you need limitations then simply use the application resource or extend it to your own needs.</p>

